---
/** Cinematic, full-bleed hero with editorial overlay */
---

<section class="relative min-h-[78vh] border-b border-white/10 md:min-h-[85vh]">
  <div class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
      src="/images/photo-8.png"
      alt=""
      role="presentation"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      width={1280}
      height={899}
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/70 to-black/30 md:bg-gradient-to-r md:from-black md:via-black/55 md:to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative flex min-h-[78vh] flex-col justify-end px-4 pb-16 pt-32 md:min-h-[85vh] md:justify-center md:pb-0 md:pt-0">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl md:pb-20">
      <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-white/70 md:text-xs">Greater Vancouver Magician</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-display-cinematic)] font-semibold leading-[0.98] text-white">
        <span class="block max-w-[22ch] text-[clamp(1.65rem,4.2vw,2.65rem)] leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">
          Experience the Art of Astonishment
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-lg text-lg font-light leading-snug text-white/90 md:text-xl">
        Hello, I&apos;m Geo and I&apos;m a close-up magician.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-base font-light leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-lg">
        Elevate your events with mind-bending illusions and unforgettable moments of wonder. Perfect for corporate events, private parties, and
        special celebrations.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="#book"
          class="inline-flex min-h-12 min-w-[11rem] items-center justify-center border border-white/30 bg-white/10 px-8 text-sm font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur transition hover:bg-white hover:text-black"
        >
          Check Availability
        </a>
        <a
          href="#services"
          class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold text-white/90 underline-offset-8 hover:underline"
        >
          Learn More
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-white/10 bg-black py-16 md:py-20" aria-labelledby="cin-subheading">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-center">
    <h2 id="cin-subheading" class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display-cinematic)] text-2xl text-white md:text-3xl">
      Close-up magic that creates genuine reactions
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/65 md:text-base">
      Close-up, strolling magic is an interactive experience where the magic happens right in the hands of your guests. As I move from group to
      group, I perform mind-blowing illusions with cards, coins, and everyday objects, creating personal moments of astonishment. It&apos;s the
      perfect way to break the ice, spark conversations, and leave a lasting impression at any event.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
